
IDE: Intellij

Requirements: Docker, Java JDK 17 ,Maven 3.8.5, Google Chrome latest version

Steps to run:
1) run command: docker pull selenoid/chrome:latest
2) run command: docker compose up -d
3) move browser.json to C:\DockerVolumes\Test\Seleniod
4) run command: docker compose up -d
5) run ChromeLocalSuite.xml or ChromeRemoteSuite.xml


AutoConfig steps for Windows environments:
Just double-click "AutoConfig.bat"

Results:
Reports be found in the "test-output" folder inside "ChromeLocalSuite" and "ChromeRemoteSuite" folders
Videos for remote executions can be found in "C:\DockerVolumes\Test\Seleniod\video"